name: Vintage Lace Leggings with Double Ruffles - Pink
description:
Vintage Lace Leggings with Double Ruffles - Pink

These super trendy Lace Leggings are so adorable and excellent quality! Made out of super soft and stretchy lace. These are perfect for layering under any dress or skirt! Elastic waist.

Choose your size: 
Small fits 1-2 Years 
Medium fits 2-4 Years 
Large fits 4-6 Years

These leggings come in three colors - white, pink, and black, please check other listings for the other colors. 

Ship in 1-3 business days.
